00:24:34.550 --> 00:24:36.950
How are we doing time-wise?

00:24:36.950 --> 00:24:40.510
Oh, yes, we have time
for another question.

00:24:40.510 --> 00:24:46.180
[ Inaudible ]

00:24:46.180 --> 00:24:49.990
&gt;&gt; Jerry Pinkney: You might
have to help me, I can't --

00:24:49.990 --> 00:24:51.560
when did I start drawing?

00:24:51.560 --> 00:24:53.720
How old are you?

00:24:53.720 --> 00:24:57.990
Six? Yeah, I started when I
was probably -- you know what?

00:24:57.990 --> 00:25:01.750
To tell you the truth, I
think I started as soon

00:25:01.750 --> 00:25:06.120
