to mark with and mark on.

00:25:06.120 --> 00:25:08.110
And by the way, mark on --

00:25:08.110 --> 00:25:11.270
at one point I just have
to tell you a little bit

00:25:11.270 --> 00:25:13.320
about my father's encouragement.

00:25:13.320 --> 00:25:14.620
I was on a bunk bed.

00:25:14.620 --> 00:25:16.170
I had the top bunk.

00:25:16.170 --> 00:25:17.470
And guess what?

00:25:17.470 --> 00:25:20.320
I would sometimes draw on the wall.

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:25.040
But however -- this is it --
